description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News & ParaShare Terrified Toddler & Ghost Bride Edition!

Dave & Tim explore the possibilities of escaping space time with the help of CIA research, encounter something under a bed with a taste for toddlers, have a sighting of a Ghost Bride, and share YOUR real encounters with the supernatural and listener questions.

All that PLUS a Brand New Theater of the Mind.
